<varlistentry id="options.StickyBevel">
	<term>StickyBevel</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Style used when defining the Bevel appearance for Sticky windows (those windows tagged as Sticky that appear on all views and desktops).</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Bevel#synopsis">Bevel flags</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
